questions.question: An object o0 is yellow. Then, in a segment lasting at least 5 frames, an object o1 is in front of another shpere o2, which is to the left of o0 and on the left part of the video frame. Finally, for a duration of at least 15 frames, o1 is on the left side, o0 is on the right side, and o2 is at the top of the frame.
questions.dsl: Color(o0, 'yellow'); Duration((FrontOf(o1, o2), LeftOf(o2, o0), Left(o2), Shape(o2, 'sphere')), 5); Duration((Left(o1), Right(o0), Top(o2)), 15)

questions.question: An object o0 is in front of another object o1 for at least 10 frames. Following that, o1 is in front of a third object o2 while o0 is on the left side of the frame, o2 is made of rubber and is at the top of the frame. Finally, for a duration of at least 15 frames, o0 is red and object o1 is on the right side of the frame.
questions.dsl: Duration(FrontOf(o0, o1), 10); (FrontOf(o1, o2), Left(o0), Material(o2, 'rubber'), Top(o2)); Duration((Color(o0, 'red'), Right(o1)), 15)

questions.question: For at least 10 frames, an object o0 is in front of another object o1. Following that, object o2 moves in front of o0 and o1 is near o2. Finally, in a sequence that lasts at least 5 frames, o0 is in front of o2, and o1 is made of rubber, with o2 situated at the top of the frame.

questions.question: An object o0 is in front of another object o1, which is made of rubber, while a third object o2 is on the left side of the video frame. questions.question: o1 is to the left of a green object o0. Then, for at least 10 frames, o0 is far away from o1, a third object o2 is in front of o1, and o1 is at the top of the frame. questions.question: For at least 10 frames, an object o0 is simultaneously behind another object o1 and in front of a third object o2, with o1 being at the top of the frame. Following that, o1 and o2 are both on the left side of the video frame and are made of rubber material.
